# This repo holds only original work: tooling, hand-written C, symbols, notes.
# The ROM, NitroFS assets, and anything extracted from a cartridge dump stay
# local. Do not force-add these patterns. Do not commit "just this one file."
# =============================================================================

# --- Retail ROM and dumps ---
