# Keep intentional project docs images under docs/ only; ignore root dumps:
/*.png
/*.bmp
/*.jpg
/*.jpeg
/*.gif
/*.tga
/*.ico

# --- Banner binary / icon data if generated ---
banner/*.bin
*.banner

# --- dsd / ndstool extract products that enumerate ROM contents ---
# path_order is a full NitroFS file list from the dump — keep local.
path_order.txt
# Header fields (title/gamecode) come from the ROM; keep local until you
# re-author a clean project config under config/.
header.yaml
# Root config.yaml from a raw unpack points at local bins/assets; prefer a
# cleaned copy under config/ when you are ready to track rebuild metadata.
# Uncomment if you want the unpack config ignored too:
# /config.yaml

# --- Ghidra / IDA / Binary Ninja local databases (often embed binary data) ---
ghidra_out/
ghidra_projects/
ghidra_targets.txt
